{"type": "article", "id": 2251, "title": "手工吹制玻璃杯", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-08T17:37:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060522231148qnItCdF2Wf73jJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰埃因霍恩设计学院（ Design Academy Eindhoven ）的学生 Florence Louisy 与 Léo Schlumberger 日前推出了一款由手工吹制玻璃制成的 alliance glass collection ，目的是为了帮助用户在喝酒时避免摄入过多的酒精。这款杯具由一大一小两个杯子组成，一个杯子用来盛放酒精饮品，另一个用来装水，将小杯子叠放在大杯子里。设计师的初衷是用这种最为自然的方式，希望能够鼓励用户在饮酒时配以适量的水，有助于防止酒精的过度摄入。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222308yYtkwuhQSaM03PX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052223096FHbzmVC8JMe0jwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222309F9rk1sSyBzZJvL6Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222310sJxhCK9vVNWRioyg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}